  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Restore hope for 1,200 widows in Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project plans to provide land titles to 1,200 hopeless and marginalized Burundian households made of widows and orphans at risks, traumatized by injustice and extreme poverty, caused by spoliation; the grabbing of their land holdings; bad judgments from  courts and plots boundaries&apos; recurring conflicts. 60 women will be trained in Human Rights, Gender-Based Violence and provided with legal texts so as to know their rights, spread them and be capable to raise their voices against injustice</narrative>
  </description>
